title: Twitter's Jack Dorsey to Give Employees Nearly $200 Million in Stock
text:
Twitter's Jack Dorsey to Give Employees Nearly $200 Million in Stock 
Published By: Entrepeneur - Today 
The move comes as Dorsey works to rebuild employee morale at Twitter after a series of high-level departures over the last few months....
